title: Ornament, one of a pair
description: one of a pair of ornaments, nine-petaled rosette with nine whorls radiating from it; inlay of jade, turquoise, pearl and shell (?); traces of wood on back; sheet gold, repousse over bronze, granulation.
creditline: Gift of Mrs. Charles S. Pillsbury, Phillip Winston Pillsbury, Mary Stinson Pillsbury Lord, Katherine Stevens Pillsbury McKee and Helen Winston Pillsbury Becker in memory of Charles S. Pillsbury
